<body>
    <h1>Development Flow</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p><br></p>
<p>Following diagram shows the various life cycle activities a typical feat=
ure goes thru, before it reaches the end user</p>
<p><map id=3D"gliffy-map-1869524976-4023" name=3D"gliffy-map-1869524976-402=
3"></map></p>
<table width=3D"100%" class=3D"gliffy-macro-table">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<table class=3D"gliffy-macro-inner-table">
<caption align=3D"bottom">
</caption>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><img style=3D"border: none; width: 956px;" usemap=3D"#gliffy-map-186952=
