></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Please use your Squad Scrum Board to view and track your assigned storie=
s/tasks. Sprints are two weeks, from Wednesday to 2nd Tuesday EOD.</p>
<p>NOTE:</p>
<ul>
<li>You are expected to update your story status by moving across various l=
anes on the board, before the stand up!</li>
<li>Pls make sure your story is assigned for testing at least the <strong>F=
riday</strong> before the end of sprint so there is enough time for testing=
</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
