<th scope=3D"col" class=3D"confluenceTh">Board</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Channels (Customer Portal)</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://jira.=
srv.westpac.com.au/secure/RapidBoard.jspa?rapidView=3D93957&amp;projectKey=
