<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"DevelopmentFlow-DoDDefinitionofDone"><span class=3D"confluence-an=
chor-link" id=3D"DevelopmentFlow-DoD"></span><a href=3D"#DevelopmentFlow-Do=
D">Definition of Done</a></h2>
<ul>
<li>Pull assigned story in sprint into "In Progress" lane</li>
<li>Development/Coding complete</li>
<li>Unit Tests created/updated</li>
<li>Create Pull Request (PR)&nbsp;</li>
<li>Review &amp; Merge PR</li>
<li>Deploy to SIT (INT or E2E) environment</li>
<li>QA System Testing=20
<ul>
<li>if part of the story, occasionally DEV-ONLY stories are created if dev =
effort greater than 5 SP, recommend to split dev &amp; testing to another s=
tory when possible</li>
<li>No issues OR Defects created to track in another sprint (if issues can'=
t be resolved in current sprint)</li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p>Jira Statuses:&nbsp;<span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge">TO DO</span=
> =E2=86=92 <span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-current">IN=
 PROGRESS</span> =E2=86=92 <span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge">FUNNEL<=
/span> (<span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><strong>BLOCKED</strong></span=
>) OR <span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-current">IN REVIE=
W</span> =E2=86=92 <span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-curr=
ent">IN TEST</span> =E2=86=92 <span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-l=
ozenge-success">DONE</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Jira Sprint Board</p>
