<h2 id=3D"DevelopmentFlow-DependencyTracking">Dependency Tracking</h2>
<p>Quite often your stories/tasks could be dependent on others. You can vie=
w the dependencies in the <span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><strong>Iss=
ue Links </strong>section.</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">You can also see a visual dependen=
cy map here: &nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,82,204);"><a href=3D"https:/=
/jira.srv.westpac.com.au/secure/PortfolioPlanView.jspa?id=3D12037&amp;sid=
=3D12123&amp;vid=3D6763#plan/dependencies" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"n=
ofollow">Dependencies report</a></span></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);"><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,82,204=
);"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-man=
ual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image" draggable=3D"false" heig=
ht=3D"111" src=3D"170b3a1e4c1daa55b19ccf41d3bf762ff76ddae1dabd04893ab8bdc24=
5a449bc" data-image-src=3D"/download/attachments/1869524978/image-2024-11-4=
_22-0-18.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1730718018297&amp;api=3Dv2"=
 data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1869525387"=
 data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment=
