ipals</a> (Definition of Done etc)</li>
<li><p class=3D"with-breadcrumbs"><u><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.west=
pac.com.au/display/ARTC/Agile+Delivery" rel=3D"nofollow">Agile Delivery</a>=
</u></p>
<ul>
<li><p class=3D"with-breadcrumbs"><u><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.west=
pac.com.au/display/ARTC/Squad+Delivery+Model" rel=3D"nofollow">Squad Delive=
ry Model</a></u></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<p><br></p>
